{
  "stem": "25639.7",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she said her husband was a judge in Germany.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And because of his political philosophies, he was taken from his job, and he was sent to Poland.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He didn't like it in Poland, and so they sent him back to Germany.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he worked at the underground factory on the V1 and V2 missile project.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he used to come home, she wrote, telling her that-- that-- it is-- it is unbelievable to what extent human beings could be reduced.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They are so emaciated, they're so raggedy, they are so exhausted that they fall asleep on their jobs.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And-- and they don't give them anything to eat to speak of.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And so she was so taken by his description of us, that from then on, she packed an extra lunch to share with somebody.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And she thinks that it was her husband who shared his lunch with me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Now, I think that's wonderful.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And whether or not it was this lady's husband, I have much feelings for this person and-- and the way he took his life in his own hands to do this.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He just left it there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He took a bite into his lunch and he just left it there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he didn't tell me, but there was sign language through eyes that I may go and eat that which he left there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So I had to be careful, of course, to eat it discreetly, because I'm not supposed to be eating except what they gave me officially.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So it was a very interesting experience many years later for me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I also have another little story about-- that-- that is relating-- that relates to this Beendorf.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
